title: TerraZen Centre
typeOfFood: Vegan, Japanese, Organic, Western, Caribbean, Fusion
description: Vegan food cafe near Dam square. Menu combines Caribbean and Japanese tastes and ingredients to create its unique dishes. Sample menu items like the house-made vegan burger, quinoa salad, fresh spring rolls, udon noodle, hijiki seaweed salad, and vegan desserts. Uses local organic produce. Beverages offered include fruit shakes, tea, and coffee. Hosts special events. Additional phone numbers 0203377078, 0629086271.
